{"tid":587362,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"[賭博心得] 記住賭錢時，唔好飲咖啡 /  濃茶","createTime":"2018-03-10T11:17:09.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-10T12:10:52.000Z","uid":123335,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"5fc314c04374dc2d8c385b211806674a1d981ce9","tid":587362,"uid":123335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-10T11:17:09.000Z","msg":"有冇發覺<br />\n一飲親咖啡 /  濃茶 ，都會必輸<br />\n知唔知點解？<br />\n<br />\n因為受當中咖啡因影響<br />\n飲後大腦血管收窄，腦血流量減少<br />\n根本係不利思考<br />\n<br />\n雖然係有提神同focus 既作用<br />\n但提神只係令到你眼光光focus 埋d 無用既資料<br />\ne.g. 你賭馬時就令你過份focus 單一資訊如場地讀數 , 反而睇唔清個big picture <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n另外咖啡因亦有壯膽既作用<br />\n令你拎住個眼光狹窄既分析結果<br />\n大大膽咁去投注<br />\n<br />\n所以，<br />\n飲完咖啡 /  濃茶 去賭錢<br />\n最尾通常都係輸"},{"pid":"41e11d50ddc21a7ef3f9e72a9c19b09fd4ea8ac7","tid":587362,"uid":123335,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-10T11:22:09.000Z","msg":"要飲就飲水<br />\n真正補充水份俾大腦<br />\n<br />\n濃茶，咖啡呢d <br />\n就留係你贏左錢之後先飲返杯黎慶祝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90a6d58d021b7285a279eb025141a1855f315cf8","tid":587362,"uid":123335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-10T11:25:43.000Z","msg":"巴打有冇補充<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d192fa90c3ce9c12f4a8a8d447ec5cae0dbf2f5","tid":587362,"uid":40588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-10T11:28:37.000Z","msg":"1000"},{"pid":"33faa52e13ae9e4eec1842f46d4b370ece1d49bb","tid":587362,"uid":28307,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-10T11:29:38.000Z","msg":"絕對認同 個腦明明唔清醒唔醒目 <br />\n但要靠咖啡嚟提神 <br />\n會極易因為高估自己 而做錯決定<br />\n有時心智狀態唔清醒 根本唔應該賭錢or炒野"},{"pid":"9159dfeb3e4452832493b4fd2ced448df04c4036","tid":587362,"uid":123335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9d192fa90c3ce9c12f4a8a8d447ec5cae0dbf2f5","tid":587362,"uid":40588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-10T11:28:37.000Z","msg":"1000"},"citedBy":0,